title: File:Australian soldiers with the 5th Battalion, Royal Australian Regiment march in an Anzac Day parade in Darwin, Australia, April 25, 2013 130425-M-AL626-013.jpg
author: 2ndLt Savannah Moyer
description: Australian soldiers with the 5th Battalion, Royal Australian Regiment march in an Anzac Day parade in Darwin, Australia, April 25, 2013. Anzac Day commemorates Australian and New Zealand military personnel who served in all wars, conflicts and peacekeeping operations.
